OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777306271
OL,3,CM4 closed after lorry crash leaves
OL,4,Cprosecco scattered across carriageway
OL,6,FThe M4 motorway has been closed
OL,7,Fwestbound between junctions 13
OL,8,F(Chieveley/Newbury) and 14
OL,9,F(Hungerford) due to a collision
OL,10,Finvolving two HGVs.
OL,12,FOne of the vehicles was carrying 20
OL,13,Ftonnes of Lovelli Prosecco which is
OL,14,Fnow spread across the carriageway,
OL,15,Fleaving significant debris and smashed
OL,16,Fglass throughout.
OL,18,FThe other vehicle has had its (empty)
OL,19,Fshipping container knocked off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
