PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777306271
OL,3,CM4 closed after lorry crash leaves
OL,4,Cprosecco scattered across carriageway
OL,6,FIn a Facebook post, Thames Valley
OL,7,FPolice wrote: "One driver is under
OL,8,Finvestigation for dangerous driving,
OL,9,Fwith early indications suggesting
OL,10,Fmobile phone use at the wheel."
OL,12,FThey added: "Amazingly only minor
OL,13,Finjuries received by one of the
OL,14,Fdrivers!"
OL,16,FEmergency services, including Thames
OL,17,FValley Police, are in attendance.
OL,19,FNational Highways Traffic Officers are
OL,20,Falso on scene assisting with traffic
OL,21,Fmanagement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
