OL,3,CM4 closed after lorry crash leaves
OL,4,Cprosecco scattered across carriageway
OL,6,FRecovery is expected to be prolonged
OL,7,Fand complex.
OL,9,FThe following diversion route is in
OL,10,Fplace:
OL,12,FDrivers are being advised to allow
OL,13,Fextra journey time, meanwhile further
OL,14,Finformation is available from National
OL,15,FHighways by visiting
OL,16,Fwww.trafficengland.com.
